WEBVTT

01:37.860 --> 01:41.020
[The Epoch of Miyu]

01:41.090 --> 01:43.960
[Episode 33]

01:52.729 --> 01:55.789
I want you to be personally
responsible for my company.

01:56.360 --> 01:57.380
Stop it.

01:59.830 --> 02:01.480
This is your first large order

02:01.480 --> 02:02.880
in the Sales Department.

02:03.090 --> 02:04.150
Congratulations.

02:07.250 --> 02:10.039
[Hotel Sales Report]

02:10.039 --> 02:11.310
[Statement of Expenditures]

02:24.190 --> 02:25.310
This is

02:25.890 --> 02:27.870
an annual exam-taker dividend.

02:28.310 --> 02:29.550
Ji Feng

02:29.570 --> 02:31.420
could only get it once.

02:32.410 --> 02:33.850
Mr. Wei, don't worry.

02:39.240 --> 02:40.840
What about the boat pastries

02:41.200 --> 02:42.800
and the Chinese restaurant?

02:43.400 --> 02:44.800
Are these all dividends?

02:45.280 --> 02:46.829
The profit is 10% now,

02:47.450 --> 02:49.579
and it's heading for 20% next quarter.

02:49.960 --> 02:51.470
Don't forget our agreement with Kuanli.

02:51.470 --> 02:53.280
It requires 30%.

02:53.630 --> 02:55.440
Tell me what to do!

03:01.430 --> 03:03.640
We can look down on our opponents,

03:03.850 --> 03:04.900
but in action,

03:05.400 --> 03:06.750
we must always go all out.

03:06.750 --> 03:07.710
Mr. Qian.

03:08.150 --> 03:09.000
Yes.

03:10.120 --> 03:11.780
Please rest assured, Mr. Wei.

03:14.680 --> 03:15.750
I promise.

03:16.750 --> 03:17.630
Ji Feng

03:17.870 --> 03:19.750
will only be happy for a moment.

03:20.150 --> 03:20.630
Later,

03:21.150 --> 03:22.480
I'll teach him a lesson.

03:24.630 --> 03:25.240
Okay.

03:26.000 --> 03:27.000
I'll wait and see.

03:28.050 --> 03:33.800
[Art Talk]

03:28.890 --> 03:29.840
I'm almost done with this.

03:29.840 --> 03:30.800
All right. Come over later

03:30.800 --> 03:31.960
and help me take down the bottom.

03:31.960 --> 03:32.360
Okay.

03:33.680 --> 03:34.680
It's so tight.

03:33.800 --> 03:36.690
[Curator: GIULIA]

03:36.079 --> 03:36.870
Okay.

03:37.430 --> 03:39.030
All right, that's it for now.

03:46.880 --> 03:47.930
Hello.

03:47.970 --> 03:49.800
I thought this forum was on Friday.

03:49.800 --> 03:51.280
Why are you taking it down now?

03:51.280 --> 03:52.400
It's canceled.

03:52.400 --> 03:53.710
That's impossible.

03:53.880 --> 03:55.910
My colleagues are in charge of this event.

03:55.910 --> 03:57.520
They were having a meeting
about it yesterday.

03:57.520 --> 03:59.150
Well, we received a notice from leaders

03:59.150 --> 04:00.280
that it's canceled.

04:17.430 --> 04:18.360
You're all here.

04:18.600 --> 04:20.660
Don't you need to go out for business?

04:21.120 --> 04:22.160
Don't mention it.

04:22.060 --> 04:25.240
[Purong Hotel]

04:23.240 --> 04:25.840
I don't know what happened to
Mr. Qian lately.

04:25.870 --> 04:28.390
He rejected proposals
like rejecting blind dates.

04:28.390 --> 04:29.680
This one needed improvement,

04:29.680 --> 04:31.140
and that one got rejected.

04:31.570 --> 04:33.030
There's no work left to do.

04:33.040 --> 04:34.770
Having work isn't much better.

04:34.920 --> 04:36.070
I managed to get

04:36.070 --> 04:37.390
a deal from a high-end tour group.

04:37.390 --> 04:38.630
Things were going well,

04:38.630 --> 04:39.390
but right before signing the agreement,

04:39.390 --> 04:41.120
Mr. Qian suddenly changed his mind.

04:41.120 --> 04:41.980
I asked around,

04:42.159 --> 04:43.360
and guess what?

04:43.560 --> 04:44.720
Do we even need to guess?

04:44.720 --> 04:46.120
They went to Kuanli.

04:46.560 --> 04:47.680
It's not just you.

04:47.700 --> 04:49.870
Recently, several colleagues' orders

04:49.870 --> 04:52.040
were inexplicably snatched by Kuanli.

04:52.040 --> 04:53.159
Believe it or not,

04:53.159 --> 04:54.840
the Q4 performance

04:54.870 --> 04:58.070
will be worse than those in the rainy
and typhoon seasons.

04:59.950 --> 05:02.240
Aren't we going to think of a solution?

05:03.270 --> 05:04.530
What can we do?

05:04.830 --> 05:06.210
The bosses are slacking off.

05:06.210 --> 05:07.510
We are just nobody.

05:07.510 --> 05:09.110
Why should we worry about it?

05:10.830 --> 05:12.070
I heard

05:12.070 --> 05:15.060
Mr. Qian and Mr. Ji are
fighting against each other.

05:15.380 --> 05:17.440
He is obviously embarrassing Mr. Ji.

05:17.830 --> 05:20.470
The one-year VAM agreement is almost up.

05:20.800 --> 05:23.550
Mr. Ji is under a lot of pressure.

05:24.650 --> 05:25.520
Let's go.

05:33.040 --> 05:34.920
The deadline for the VAM agreement
is approaching.

05:34.920 --> 05:36.650
Is the hotel doing well lately?

05:37.310 --> 05:38.830
It's fine. Don't worry.

05:39.270 --> 05:40.600
Why do you suddenly ask?

05:41.390 --> 05:42.510
I heard that Qian Xun has been

05:42.510 --> 05:44.630
obstructing the Sales
Department's orders lately.

05:44.630 --> 05:46.159
Is there anything I can do to help you?

05:46.159 --> 05:47.600
You're dealing with

05:47.600 --> 05:49.159
Qian Xun and Lu Zhenzhen
in the Sales Department.

05:49.159 --> 05:50.820
Actually, you're helping me.

05:53.950 --> 05:56.510
What? Don't you believe in your boyfriend?

06:00.480 --> 06:02.280
All right, don't worry too much.

06:02.680 --> 06:03.690
Go on up.

06:04.480 --> 06:05.560
Be careful.

06:11.000 --> 06:11.800
Miyu.

06:11.800 --> 06:14.040
I heard you're no longer
in the Front Office.

06:14.040 --> 06:15.100
So I came to see you.

06:15.190 --> 06:16.430
Want to eat together?

06:17.120 --> 06:19.250
Okay, we can talk while having dinner.

06:20.430 --> 06:22.800
Two wonton noodles, please.

06:23.830 --> 06:24.310
Okay.

06:31.070 --> 06:32.420
Have I gotten tanned

06:32.600 --> 06:34.070
from running field errands?

06:34.070 --> 06:34.830
No.

06:35.360 --> 06:36.720
You're not holding a walkie-talkie

06:36.720 --> 06:38.360
or wearing a uniform anymore.

06:38.360 --> 06:39.830
It's so good

06:40.830 --> 06:41.690
to be yourself.

06:42.720 --> 06:44.720
I remember the first time I met you,

06:45.510 --> 06:48.040
you were like a frightened bird,

06:48.180 --> 06:49.510
trying desperately to please

06:49.510 --> 06:50.720
everyone around you.

06:50.920 --> 06:52.510
But after that, every time I saw you,

06:52.510 --> 06:54.970
I found you a little different
from the last,

06:55.510 --> 06:57.060
more confident,

06:57.600 --> 06:59.750
happier,

07:00.160 --> 07:01.680
bolder,

07:01.830 --> 07:02.510
and more…

07:02.950 --> 07:05.350
Anyway, you're getting better and better.

07:06.120 --> 07:07.920
You seem to enjoy your work.

07:08.560 --> 07:09.720
I truly feel

07:10.270 --> 07:12.330
this can be my lifelong stage.

07:12.720 --> 07:14.800
There is a lot of scheming

07:14.800 --> 07:15.920
and deception,

07:15.920 --> 07:16.630
but

07:16.950 --> 07:18.480
these underhanded tricks

07:18.480 --> 07:20.610
are not the core of the hotel industry.

07:21.040 --> 07:23.100
The true spirit of the hotel industry

07:23.430 --> 07:24.850
is always

07:25.160 --> 07:26.690
making guests feel at home,

07:26.800 --> 07:28.800
which is the best metaphor for life.

07:32.270 --> 07:33.000
Miyu,

07:33.190 --> 07:34.120
I really envy you

07:34.390 --> 07:36.320
for finding your own stage in life.

07:41.159 --> 07:43.360
Is something on your mind, Mr. Tan?

07:44.120 --> 07:45.360
No, nothing.

07:45.360 --> 07:46.960
Just a spontaneous thought.

07:58.130 --> 08:01.850
[Tan Jizhou]

08:04.170 --> 08:06.450
[Tan Jizhou]

08:08.460 --> 08:09.310
[Revealing exhibition of
Golden Times]

08:09.330 --> 08:10.010
[of independent curator
Tan Jizhou delays infinitely]

08:10.030 --> 08:11.080
[Tan Jizhou's exhibition hall is pending]

08:11.100 --> 08:12.360
[Independent curator Tan Jizhou's
divorce gossip]

08:17.570 --> 08:19.930
[Tan Jizhou's exhibition is
in trouble with uncertain future]

08:19.980 --> 08:21.100
[Today, a piece of pitiful news is]

08:21.130 --> 08:22.520
[spreading on various platforms.]

08:24.610 --> 08:25.710
[It is reported that
the exhibition hall is]

08:25.740 --> 08:26.950
[still pending. This has brought
a lot of uncertainties]

08:26.970 --> 08:28.240
[to the exhibition plan]

08:40.720 --> 08:41.580
Mr. Tan.

08:44.910 --> 08:45.390
Please.

08:45.390 --> 08:45.840
Okay.

08:50.030 --> 08:52.900
I'm surprised you asked me out.

08:54.790 --> 08:57.590
-I wish I hadn’t taken up much time.
-Of course not.

08:57.600 --> 08:58.360
What's up?

08:59.630 --> 09:01.840
I heard you were going to
hold an art exhibition.

09:01.840 --> 09:04.840
So I searched for the news online

09:04.840 --> 09:06.270
and found out

09:06.720 --> 09:08.110
your exhibition

09:08.110 --> 09:09.550
isn't going well.

09:10.600 --> 09:11.360
Thank you

09:11.360 --> 09:13.090
for worrying about my affairs.

09:13.840 --> 09:14.960
The situation is

09:14.960 --> 09:16.030
a bit complicated.

09:17.030 --> 09:18.150
In short,

09:18.150 --> 09:20.080
I'm not satisfied with

09:20.320 --> 09:21.580
the hotel in Hong Kong.

09:22.130 --> 09:24.120
Could you tell me why?

09:24.180 --> 09:25.190
Of course.

09:26.200 --> 09:27.010
The thing is,

09:27.270 --> 09:29.490
they couldn't provide the space I want.

09:29.720 --> 09:30.960
But my core team

09:30.960 --> 09:32.200
wanted me to compromise

09:32.200 --> 09:34.800
because they've already
paid a hefty deposit.

09:36.910 --> 09:39.150
What kind of space do you want?

09:42.750 --> 09:45.100
Flowing, non-standardized

09:45.130 --> 09:46.800
and time-honored.

09:46.820 --> 09:49.030
The theme of my curation this time
is called

09:49.030 --> 09:49.790
"Time",

09:50.000 --> 09:50.910
so I really

09:50.910 --> 09:52.480
want to present a feeling of

09:52.480 --> 09:53.580
time flowing.

09:53.610 --> 09:54.840
But right now, this venue

09:54.840 --> 09:56.780
is as boring as a matchbox.

09:56.810 --> 09:58.140
Actually, I just want to

09:58.160 --> 09:59.710
break its boxy feel

09:59.750 --> 10:01.390
and add some dynamic installations.

10:01.390 --> 10:02.150
But I don't know why

10:02.150 --> 10:04.150
everyone thinks I'm dreaming.

10:06.320 --> 10:08.650
By everyone, you mean?

10:08.750 --> 10:10.000
The venue manager,

10:10.000 --> 10:11.030
my core team,

10:11.030 --> 10:12.120
and my CFO.

10:13.510 --> 10:14.550
Miss Lin Nanxin.

10:18.820 --> 10:20.620
You've really read a lot of news.

10:22.390 --> 10:23.000
Yes.

10:23.910 --> 10:25.440
She is my ex-wife.

10:26.060 --> 10:27.150
Actually, in our careers,

10:27.150 --> 10:28.870
we are so compatible

10:29.150 --> 10:31.390
that we had to break up our family

10:32.030 --> 10:32.790
and devote all our energy to

10:32.790 --> 10:34.520
building our curatorial team.

10:35.550 --> 10:38.350
But this time she also thought
I'm messing around.

10:38.780 --> 10:40.180
I don't have any choices.

10:42.080 --> 10:44.790
What if we change the approach?

10:45.440 --> 10:46.370
What do you mean?

10:47.480 --> 10:48.910
Do you have time

10:48.970 --> 10:50.670
to listen to my idea?

10:50.670 --> 10:51.480
Of course.

10:52.040 --> 10:55.450
[Jixuan Hall] [Bilan Hall]

10:55.030 --> 10:56.510
Purong has such a place?

10:56.750 --> 10:58.720
Your theme is time,

10:58.740 --> 11:00.200
so I thought of this place.

11:01.000 --> 11:02.600
Purong Hotel records

11:02.600 --> 11:04.600
the memories of several generations.

11:04.600 --> 11:07.510
Whether in terms of architectural style
or cultural heritage,

11:07.510 --> 11:09.510
it quite matches

11:09.510 --> 11:11.710
the sense of accumulated time you want.

11:11.720 --> 11:12.320
Yes.

11:13.750 --> 11:15.440
Indeed, the venues in Hong Kong

11:15.440 --> 11:16.360
are too modern

11:16.360 --> 11:17.620
and too standardized.

11:18.200 --> 11:19.000
In this way,

11:19.000 --> 11:19.750
Purong's style

11:19.750 --> 11:21.750
really fits my idea.

11:22.630 --> 11:24.690
But this space…

11:25.600 --> 11:26.240
These two

11:26.240 --> 11:28.040
are our two small banquet halls.

11:28.330 --> 11:30.050
They are not square,

11:28.500 --> 11:32.020
[Jixuan Hall] [Bilan Hall]

11:30.080 --> 11:32.240
so they are not used frequently.

11:32.510 --> 11:33.510
But I think

11:33.510 --> 11:35.840
its irregular shape

11:35.840 --> 11:38.240
provides more wall space.

11:38.320 --> 11:38.870
In this regard,

11:38.870 --> 11:41.400
it's more beneficial
for the art exhibition.

11:41.750 --> 11:44.000
This time, we can connect the two spaces.

11:44.000 --> 11:45.000
You can use

11:45.000 --> 11:47.150
the entire space freely.

11:47.390 --> 11:49.720
In the middle, we can connect

11:49.720 --> 11:51.390
the two halls with a corridor.

11:49.770 --> 11:51.260
[Jixuan Hall] [Bilan Hall]

11:51.960 --> 11:53.720
We can put some video

11:53.720 --> 11:54.440
installations inside

11:54.440 --> 11:57.510
to create a feeling of flowing time,

11:57.510 --> 12:00.270
allowing the audience
to pass through this time tunnel

12:00.270 --> 12:01.270
to your artistic world.

12:01.270 --> 12:02.510
Sorry to interrupt.

12:04.510 --> 12:05.390
If...

12:05.390 --> 12:06.870
I mean, if I hold the exhibition...

12:06.870 --> 12:08.440
Purong Hotel is definitely perfect for it.

12:08.440 --> 12:09.320
Trust me.

12:10.200 --> 12:12.600
If you're willing to consider this space,

12:12.600 --> 12:14.240
I can take you to the field.

12:14.240 --> 12:15.840
You can do whatever you want.

12:16.230 --> 12:17.390
Really?

12:17.720 --> 12:19.240
Because this is so far

12:19.240 --> 12:20.960
the most ideal venue I've ever seen.

12:20.960 --> 12:23.200
But for a five-star hotel like Purong,

12:23.200 --> 12:25.630
I don't think turning a banquet hall
into an art exhibition

12:25.630 --> 12:27.320
serves your interests.

12:27.320 --> 12:28.600
Actually, we need

12:28.600 --> 12:30.080
this art exhibition more than you think.

12:30.080 --> 12:32.200
So I will do my best to fight for it.

12:33.200 --> 12:34.240
Thank you. Thank you.

12:34.240 --> 12:34.840
Thank you.

12:34.840 --> 12:35.480
Mr. Tan.

12:35.960 --> 12:36.840
Mr. Tan.

12:37.190 --> 12:38.030
I'm sorry.

12:38.200 --> 12:39.360
I got too excited.

12:39.380 --> 12:40.260
My apologies.

12:41.320 --> 12:42.920
Wish us a happy cooperation.

12:45.480 --> 12:47.080
Wish us a happy cooperation.

12:48.940 --> 12:49.910
I disagree.

12:50.320 --> 12:51.670
You want to

12:51.670 --> 12:53.440
enhance the hotel's influence

12:53.440 --> 12:55.300
by holding crossover art events.

12:55.760 --> 12:56.760
The idea is right.

12:56.910 --> 12:58.670
But you want to connect

12:58.670 --> 13:00.540
two underutilized banquet halls

13:00.560 --> 13:02.330
to host an art exhibition.

13:02.360 --> 13:03.840
What happens after the exhibition?

13:02.440 --> 13:04.980
[Purong Hotel]

13:03.840 --> 13:05.640
How do you plan to use this space?

13:05.790 --> 13:06.670
These two banquet halls

13:06.670 --> 13:08.440
have a poor layout

13:08.440 --> 13:10.080
and a low utilization rate

13:10.080 --> 13:11.670
due to the load-bearing walls.

13:11.670 --> 13:13.510
If we connect them now,

13:13.510 --> 13:15.360
it will look like a small art gallery.

13:15.360 --> 13:16.750
I think we can turn it into

13:16.750 --> 13:18.600
an exclusive art space for Purong Hotel.

13:18.600 --> 13:19.600
You mean

13:20.240 --> 13:21.270
making

13:21.790 --> 13:22.750
these two banquet halls

13:22.750 --> 13:24.600
into a permanent art gallery?

13:24.600 --> 13:26.200
Purong Hotel has a long history

13:26.200 --> 13:28.000
and is known for its high-end taste.

13:28.000 --> 13:29.440
Many clients choose us

13:29.440 --> 13:31.480
for our cultural heritage.

13:31.720 --> 13:34.320
Whether we host regular art exhibitions

13:34.320 --> 13:35.440
or use this space

13:35.440 --> 13:37.600
to display our hotel's

13:37.600 --> 13:38.630
cultural history,

13:38.630 --> 13:40.000
it's in the hotel's best interest.

13:40.000 --> 13:41.910
In the hotel's interest?

13:41.910 --> 13:43.960
Is your idea supported by data?

13:44.720 --> 13:46.870
We need solid data

13:46.870 --> 13:48.510
and a risk assessment

13:48.510 --> 13:49.960
to determine if a project is profitable.

13:49.960 --> 13:50.960
Let's not look too far ahead.

13:50.960 --> 13:52.450
Just discuss the exhibition itself.

13:52.450 --> 13:53.510
As for the venue setup,

13:52.490 --> 13:54.060
[Purong Hotel]

13:53.510 --> 13:54.750
the security of the exhibits,

13:54.750 --> 13:56.030
and the services during the exhibition,

13:56.030 --> 13:58.240
how much manpower
and resources are needed?

13:58.240 --> 14:00.840
Are you confident in recouping costs?

14:01.030 --> 14:02.120
Have you evaluated the value of

14:02.120 --> 14:03.510
the exhibition itself?

14:04.000 --> 14:04.720
Is it worth

14:04.910 --> 14:06.200
dedicating

14:06.200 --> 14:07.480
two banquet halls at once?

14:07.480 --> 14:08.720
I will do detailed research

14:08.720 --> 14:10.720
on all of that.

14:10.720 --> 14:12.240
But there are successful cases of

14:12.240 --> 14:13.550
hotels using art exhibitions

14:13.550 --> 14:16.070
to enhance their influence.

14:16.070 --> 14:17.790
I think we can give it a try

14:17.790 --> 14:19.030
and work to minimize the risks,

14:19.030 --> 14:20.670
instead of rejecting it

14:20.670 --> 14:21.630
without even trying.

14:21.630 --> 14:24.200
Purong Hotel is at a critical moment now.

14:24.200 --> 14:25.840
It's not a proper time for
trial and error.

14:25.840 --> 14:27.670
Because it's a critical moment for us,

14:27.670 --> 14:29.480
we should make a bold breakthrough.

14:29.480 --> 14:30.840
That's what you taught me.

14:30.840 --> 14:31.950
This is not a breakthrough,

14:31.950 --> 14:33.350
but a reckless movement.

14:34.510 --> 14:35.790
I thought you would support me.

14:35.790 --> 14:37.030
Do you want me to

14:37.060 --> 14:38.910
support you unconditionally

14:38.910 --> 14:40.080
even if knowing your proposal
is highly risky?

14:40.080 --> 14:41.200
What do you mean?

14:41.200 --> 14:42.240
I'm talking about work.

14:42.240 --> 14:43.960
Me too.

14:57.030 --> 14:58.240
I want to support you.

14:59.400 --> 15:01.590
But the internal strife is too fierce.

15:01.610 --> 15:03.290
I don't want you to be the target.

15:03.290 --> 15:05.470
What's your point of saying that,

15:05.490 --> 15:06.970
boss or boyfriend?

15:11.360 --> 15:13.320
Am I vulnerable in your eyes?

15:15.000 --> 15:17.120
I will prove that

15:17.140 --> 15:19.200
the art exhibition is worth holding.

15:26.620 --> 15:29.270
[Purong Hotel Staff Apartment]

15:29.370 --> 15:33.850
[Image-type Curation Cases]

15:43.160 --> 15:44.500
[Missed Calls from Ji Feng]

15:46.170 --> 15:48.760
[Ji Feng]

15:49.060 --> 15:50.100
[I'm almost at the cinema.]

15:50.130 --> 15:51.300
[Where are you?]

15:51.320 --> 15:52.610
[Will you come?]

16:02.140 --> 16:04.890
[Sorry. I forgot that we had arranged to
go to the cinema today.]

16:04.890 --> 16:06.700
[Sorry. I forgot that we had arranged to
go to the cinema today.]

16:07.360 --> 16:08.360
[There's a later show.]

16:08.050 --> 16:11.050
[Ji Feng]

16:09.270 --> 16:10.330
[Want to watch it?]

16:13.960 --> 16:16.200
[It's too late. Let's do it another day.]

16:14.510 --> 16:15.590
[Xu Miyu]

16:16.670 --> 16:17.390
[Okay.]

16:17.060 --> 16:19.830
[Ji Feng]

16:27.320 --> 16:29.270
[Rest early. Good night.]

16:28.610 --> 16:31.580
[Xu Miyu]

16:35.010 --> 16:39.670
[Ji Feng]

16:42.000 --> 16:50.630
[Rest early. Good night.]

16:53.320 --> 16:55.630
A disagreement at work during the day

16:55.780 --> 16:57.600
will unknowingly

16:57.630 --> 16:59.290
kill the romance of the night.

17:00.240 --> 17:01.170
Gradually,

17:01.840 --> 17:03.600
we stop trying to distinguish

17:03.600 --> 17:05.829
between love and working together.

17:06.349 --> 17:07.589
Our love

17:07.680 --> 17:09.940
is mixed with more and more rationality.

17:18.550 --> 17:19.680
What are you doing?

17:20.099 --> 17:21.520
Spacing out?

17:21.829 --> 17:22.640
No.

17:24.000 --> 17:25.329
I slept late last night.

17:27.599 --> 17:28.610
Well,

17:29.000 --> 17:31.110
Yuntian Group from New Zealand

17:31.310 --> 17:33.000
is coming to China for bidding.

17:33.000 --> 17:35.000
I heard they're coming to Shanghai.

17:35.110 --> 17:36.590
Yuntian Group?

17:37.480 --> 17:38.750
Are you talking about

17:38.750 --> 17:41.260
that energy trading group in the top 50?

17:41.720 --> 17:43.180
Rui, what's your opinion?

17:43.960 --> 17:45.160
We should go all out, of course.

17:45.160 --> 17:46.030
Just say the word,

17:46.030 --> 17:47.490
and I'll act immediately.

17:47.790 --> 17:48.270
I...

17:49.160 --> 17:50.920
I haven't thought it through yet.

17:50.920 --> 17:52.350
Our only advantage right now is that

17:52.350 --> 17:54.280
we got the information in advance.

17:54.440 --> 17:56.720
I guess we'll be caught up soon.

17:57.270 --> 17:58.240
Anyway,

17:58.240 --> 17:59.510
we should hold an internal meeting to

17:59.510 --> 18:01.270
discuss the plan first.

18:01.590 --> 18:03.050
Brainstorming is useful.

18:03.510 --> 18:04.030
Okay.

18:04.030 --> 18:06.240
I'll have Secretary Wu
notify the directors.

18:06.240 --> 18:06.880
We'll hold a meeting

18:06.880 --> 18:07.960
to sync up.

18:09.960 --> 18:10.640
No.

18:12.720 --> 18:13.640
It's past five.

18:13.640 --> 18:14.590
And it's the weekend.

18:14.590 --> 18:15.920
Next week is fine.

18:18.510 --> 18:19.310
Okay.

18:20.640 --> 18:21.510
By the way,

18:21.830 --> 18:24.640
haven't your insomnia symptoms
eased a lot?

18:25.640 --> 18:26.400
No.

18:26.720 --> 18:28.960
It's seasonal.

18:29.350 --> 18:30.270
Your insomnia

18:30.590 --> 18:31.960
is seasonal?

18:32.700 --> 18:34.860
I think you're trapped in love.

18:35.720 --> 18:37.120
Having a conflict again?

18:37.210 --> 18:38.090
No.

18:41.070 --> 18:42.130
Give me your phone.

18:43.110 --> 18:43.790
What for?

18:44.200 --> 18:46.640
You can't just rely on your mind to love.

18:46.640 --> 18:48.720
You need to explain

18:48.720 --> 18:50.110
and coax her.

18:58.740 --> 18:59.370
Wait.

19:07.850 --> 19:12.480
[Li Qiaoqi]

19:08.510 --> 19:11.170
[Come to my place after work.
I'll cook for you.]

19:11.960 --> 19:12.590
[Okay.]

19:14.450 --> 19:14.590
[Li Qiaoqi]

19:14.590 --> 19:15.620
[Ji Feng] [Are you free after work?]

19:15.790 --> 19:17.770
[Ji Feng]

19:17.770 --> 19:18.400
[Sorry. I forgot that we had arranged to
go to the cinema today.]

19:18.430 --> 19:18.910
[There's another one later.
Want to watch it?]

19:18.930 --> 19:19.700
[It's too late. Maybe another day.]

19:19.200 --> 19:20.480
[Are you free after work?]

19:19.720 --> 19:20.340
[Okay.]

19:26.110 --> 19:26.910
[Sorry.]

19:27.230 --> 19:28.560
[I have plans tonight.]

19:38.900 --> 19:40.130
[Xu Miyu]

19:40.210 --> 19:43.360
[Sorry, I have plans tonight.]

19:50.310 --> 19:51.270
I'm off work.

19:51.640 --> 19:52.770
Have a good weekend.

19:57.990 --> 20:00.110
I will treat you to a big meal.

20:00.160 --> 20:00.960
Come with me.

20:02.350 --> 20:03.000
Let's go.

20:15.350 --> 20:16.920
Six kinds of cold dishes
with aged vinegar.

20:16.920 --> 20:18.850
Try it. It's their signature dish.

20:20.750 --> 20:22.920
Don't just drink. Eat something.

20:33.240 --> 20:34.170
Why is it so sour?

20:36.240 --> 20:37.400
It's fine.

20:38.830 --> 20:40.230
Maybe your mouth is sour.

20:44.640 --> 20:45.830
We're eating.

20:46.070 --> 20:47.400
What are you hinting at?

20:47.440 --> 20:48.350
Nothing.

20:49.310 --> 20:50.310
Tell me.

20:50.670 --> 20:52.840
What happened between you and Xu Miyu?

20:54.460 --> 20:55.330
She and I

20:56.240 --> 20:57.770
had a disagreement at work.

20:57.940 --> 20:59.870
I don't know why she

21:00.240 --> 21:01.960
insisted on holding
Tan Jizhou's art exhibition

21:01.960 --> 21:03.270
at Purong Hotel.

21:04.090 --> 21:05.250
Isn't that great?

21:05.280 --> 21:07.410
Qian Xun has been

21:07.430 --> 21:09.110
giving you a hard time lately.

21:09.290 --> 21:11.310
It's a good chance to take him down a peg.

21:11.310 --> 21:12.550
It's not that simple.

21:12.920 --> 21:14.850
She is in the Sales Department now.

21:14.920 --> 21:16.750
She can't be as naive as before.

21:17.570 --> 21:18.570
Stop right there.

21:19.170 --> 21:20.640
Xu Miyu is not

21:20.640 --> 21:22.240
a naive girl.

21:22.510 --> 21:24.900
I think you're overcomplicating things.

21:26.590 --> 21:27.570
Actually, no.

21:29.030 --> 21:32.030
You're probably oversimplifying it.

21:33.150 --> 21:35.430
You're just being petty.

21:36.670 --> 21:37.470
Me?

21:37.760 --> 21:38.820
I'm petty?

21:39.990 --> 21:42.320
You might call the shots at work,

21:42.340 --> 21:44.670
but emotionally, you're inexperienced.

21:45.240 --> 21:47.990
You've worked abroad
for so many years.

21:48.550 --> 21:52.310
Haven't you handled weirder projects

21:52.310 --> 21:54.110
than hosting an art exhibition?

21:55.310 --> 21:56.310
So,

21:56.950 --> 21:58.430
think it through.

21:58.450 --> 22:01.250
Are you worried about
the risk of holding the art exhibition

22:01.250 --> 22:04.180
or the person
who is going to hold the art exhibition?

22:12.920 --> 22:14.550
Are you angry that Mr. Ji

22:14.550 --> 22:15.960
rejected your proposal

22:16.160 --> 22:17.550
or that your boyfriend didn't

22:17.550 --> 22:18.750
support your career?

22:19.890 --> 22:20.930
I don't know.

22:21.000 --> 22:22.000
Maybe both.

22:24.680 --> 22:27.270
Let me analyze it for you.

22:28.480 --> 22:31.160
Ji Feng is a devil in the workplace.

22:31.160 --> 22:33.110
You know it clearly, right?

22:35.750 --> 22:39.310
After work, you two are dating.

22:39.750 --> 22:42.070
Using date time to talk about work

22:42.070 --> 22:44.000
is highly not recommended.

22:44.680 --> 22:45.480
Agree?

22:49.140 --> 22:51.660
So, whether it's the former or the latter,

22:51.680 --> 22:53.340
there's no need to be unhappy.

22:54.310 --> 22:55.920
You're right.

22:56.310 --> 22:57.590
But

22:58.400 --> 22:59.830
we are human beings,

22:59.830 --> 23:01.640
not two machines.

23:01.960 --> 23:04.830
There is no switch
to instantly change modes.

23:05.160 --> 23:06.400
I was arguing with him

23:06.400 --> 23:08.200
in the office during the day.

23:08.720 --> 23:10.830
When we go on a date at night,

23:10.830 --> 23:12.030
how can I smile at him?

23:14.110 --> 23:17.110
Miyu, I think you should relax.

23:17.960 --> 23:20.240
No matter how many relationships you have,

23:20.240 --> 23:22.110
the process of
getting along with each other

23:22.110 --> 23:24.110
matters the most.

23:25.200 --> 23:26.200
Just like us.

23:26.590 --> 23:29.250
We've known each other
for almost thirty years.

23:29.350 --> 23:30.920
We were neighbors,

23:31.480 --> 23:32.280
best friends,

23:32.470 --> 23:33.550
classmates,

23:33.550 --> 23:34.790
and now colleagues.

23:35.400 --> 23:36.830
We almost cut ties

23:36.830 --> 23:38.270
because of a jerk.

23:38.590 --> 23:39.720
But we made up

23:39.720 --> 23:40.580
after arguing.

23:40.920 --> 23:41.960
We will always be each other’s

23:41.960 --> 23:43.400
most important partner.

23:45.830 --> 23:46.640
You are right.

23:48.640 --> 23:50.720
But objectively speaking,

23:50.960 --> 23:53.400
I completely understand your frustration.

23:53.400 --> 23:54.640
Mr. Ji

23:54.790 --> 23:56.500
seems to be good at everything,

23:56.500 --> 23:57.960
but his tongue

23:57.960 --> 23:59.550
is really annoying.

24:00.590 --> 24:01.960
I support you in training him.

24:01.960 --> 24:04.690
Start with the proposal
for this art exhibition.

24:04.790 --> 24:07.000
Let him know your vision and ability

24:07.000 --> 24:08.810
are not inferior to his at all.

24:10.590 --> 24:11.350
Yes!

24:12.400 --> 24:13.600
You can do it, Xu Miyu.

24:16.060 --> 24:17.990
[Purong Hotel Staff Apartment]

24:20.240 --> 24:21.880
A successful art exhibition

24:21.880 --> 24:24.730
is the resonance of the curator's
and the creator's souls.

24:24.730 --> 24:25.880
It is the dome and high walls

24:25.880 --> 24:28.340
blending perfectly with colors and shapes.

24:28.640 --> 24:29.720
A good curator

24:29.880 --> 24:31.130
needs to have the courage and insight

24:31.130 --> 24:33.810
to break and reconstruct art.

24:31.610 --> 24:32.120
[Hidden Island Hotel Group:
Art ExhibitionRealm]

24:32.150 --> 24:32.910
[Harmony of Art and Nature]

24:33.090 --> 24:34.910
[Art Space:Immersive Experience
of Nature and Art]

24:34.000 --> 24:35.480
Outside the world of works,

24:35.480 --> 24:36.440
he builds another artistic world

24:36.440 --> 24:39.000
with greater inclusivity.

24:54.780 --> 24:55.520
[Transformation sign of banquet halls
of Purong Hotel]

24:56.270 --> 24:57.900
[Banquet Hall] [Room]

25:06.540 --> 25:07.340
I'm sorry.

25:07.790 --> 25:09.850
I came to have a look
out of curiosity.

25:22.030 --> 25:24.030
I have investigated the risks,

25:24.030 --> 25:26.070
which are elaborated on page three.

25:26.070 --> 25:27.180
The conditions of our hotel

25:27.180 --> 25:28.980
meet their security standards.

25:27.750 --> 25:30.090
[Security Advantage]

25:29.220 --> 25:30.450
As for profitability,

25:30.450 --> 25:31.980
[Content and Layout of the Art Exhibition]

25:30.830 --> 25:32.200
Mr. Tan is hosting

25:32.200 --> 25:34.960
the global premiere of his new works.

25:34.960 --> 25:35.920
Media at home and abroad

25:35.920 --> 25:38.580
are paying close attention
to this exhibition.

25:38.750 --> 25:40.750
So, I think it can effectively

25:40.750 --> 25:42.350
bring exposure to our hotel.

25:43.350 --> 25:44.790
Why didn't you work this hard

25:44.790 --> 25:45.850
on other projects?

25:46.110 --> 25:47.350
I give my all to

25:47.350 --> 25:49.210
all the projects at Purong Hotel.

25:52.040 --> 25:54.040
Mr. Ji, you can think about it first.

25:54.070 --> 25:55.530
I'll go do something else.

25:56.240 --> 25:56.830
Wait.

26:03.030 --> 26:04.830
This proposal has convinced me.

26:05.400 --> 26:06.200
Really?

26:07.550 --> 26:08.440
You agreed?

26:09.310 --> 26:10.750
You've done so much.

26:11.000 --> 26:12.660
I can't find any fault with it.

26:12.960 --> 26:15.350
How about this?
I'll tell the HR Department

26:15.350 --> 26:17.030
to promote you to sales manager.

26:17.030 --> 26:19.090
This will make things easier for you.

26:19.440 --> 26:20.350
This time, I want to rely more on

26:20.350 --> 26:21.550
my own efforts

26:21.550 --> 26:22.720
rather than taking
a shortcut with your help.

26:22.720 --> 26:23.960
The project you are leading now

26:23.960 --> 26:25.240
is not a small one.

26:25.390 --> 26:26.720
At your current position,

26:26.720 --> 26:28.110
collaborating with other departments

26:28.110 --> 26:29.950
will inevitably involve
a lot of wrangling.

26:29.950 --> 26:30.880
I just hope

26:30.880 --> 26:31.790
you can put all your energy

26:31.790 --> 26:33.110
into this project.

26:33.130 --> 26:34.260
Don't overthink it.

26:34.510 --> 26:35.350
I understand.

26:35.640 --> 26:37.570
Thank you for your support, Mr. Ji.

26:38.110 --> 26:39.170
Keep following up.

26:45.110 --> 26:46.550
Are we making up now?

26:49.550 --> 26:51.720
Let's watch the movie

26:51.790 --> 26:53.050
we haven't seen first.

26:54.510 --> 26:55.040
Let's go.

27:07.680 --> 27:08.590
I quit.

27:08.830 --> 27:10.750
-Cindy, calm down.
-I can’t watch

27:10.750 --> 27:11.920
this project lose money.

27:11.920 --> 27:13.590
It goes against my professional ethics.

27:13.590 --> 27:13.790
No.

27:13.810 --> 27:15.180
I am not like you.

27:15.480 --> 27:16.640
I'm not an artist.

27:16.750 --> 27:18.440
My major is financial management.

27:18.440 --> 27:19.880
Please don't use your wild imagination

27:19.880 --> 27:21.590
-to challenge my knowledge and knowledge.
-Okay, I understand.

27:21.590 --> 27:23.640
But how many firsts are there in life?

27:23.640 --> 27:24.350
This is my first time

27:24.350 --> 27:26.920
appearing as both a curator and a painter.

27:26.920 --> 27:28.240
This might be the only time in my life.

27:28.240 --> 27:29.200
How can you ask me to compromise?

27:29.200 --> 27:29.960
Swallow your pride.

27:29.960 --> 27:31.420
Don't be so narcissistic.

27:31.590 --> 27:33.960
This exhibition isn't your solo show.

27:33.960 --> 27:35.000
Are you asking all of us to

27:35.000 --> 27:37.110
move to Shanghai from Hong Kong

27:37.110 --> 27:39.840
just because of the words of
a hotel salesperson?

27:47.200 --> 27:48.270
Tan Jizhou.

27:50.110 --> 27:51.760
Are you in love?

27:52.350 --> 27:54.400
Can you stop confusing the issue?

27:54.400 --> 27:55.350
If I were you,

27:55.350 --> 27:56.270
I would definitely

27:56.270 --> 27:57.940
go to Purong Hotel
for a site visit right now,

27:57.940 --> 27:59.620
instead of arguing with me here.

27:59.260 --> 28:00.860
[TAN's Art]

27:59.680 --> 28:01.000
But we don't have time.

28:03.330 --> 28:06.760
[TAN's Art]

28:18.240 --> 28:19.580
Excuse me, bosses.

28:20.000 --> 28:21.510
Purong Hotel

28:21.530 --> 28:23.850
submitted the venue planning proposal.

28:25.240 --> 28:25.960
Print it.

28:42.670 --> 28:45.760
[Interactive Experience Area]
[Interior Plan]

28:48.000 --> 28:49.160
Looks good.

28:50.540 --> 28:53.830
[Time Travel Corridor] [Inner Plan]

28:50.680 --> 28:51.240
This...

28:52.030 --> 28:54.390
The design of this corridor is quite nice.

28:56.800 --> 28:57.580
[Time Travel Corridor]

29:02.380 --> 29:03.690
This is quite reasonable.

29:03.690 --> 29:05.250
This layout is very reasonable.

29:05.250 --> 29:05.740
Right.

29:07.010 --> 29:07.480
This works.

29:07.480 --> 29:12.550
[Time Travel Corridor] [Layout Plan]

29:22.470 --> 29:24.800
[Purong Hotel's Exhibition
Venue Quotation]

29:26.310 --> 29:27.920
We can save 1.8 million.

29:31.820 --> 29:32.070
[Purong Hotel's Exhibition
Venue Quotation]

29:32.110 --> 29:33.890
[Project Payment]

29:33.970 --> 29:35.960
But we have to pay a 2 million penalty.

29:35.960 --> 29:36.960
My CFO.

29:36.960 --> 29:38.030
Let's treat this 200,000 yuan

29:38.030 --> 29:39.400
as the cost of testing the waters

29:39.400 --> 29:41.160
and our tuition as newcomers, okay?

29:41.160 --> 29:42.370
What if it's not worth it?

29:42.370 --> 29:43.830
Then, I'll accept my loss.

29:50.030 --> 29:50.830
Alright.

29:51.480 --> 29:53.270
Don't make everyone on this boat

29:53.270 --> 29:54.350
go down with you.

29:54.290 --> 29:56.420
[Chief Finance Officer, Lin Nanxin]

29:56.640 --> 29:57.550
Trust me.

30:06.400 --> 30:07.830
I wish I could

30:07.830 --> 30:10.070
mute our work group chat right now.

30:11.400 --> 30:13.000
So, I don't have to see Ji Feng

30:13.000 --> 30:14.790
stirring up trouble in it every day.

30:14.790 --> 30:16.510
When did Purong Hotel

30:16.510 --> 30:18.550
hold an art exhibition?

30:18.550 --> 30:20.160
Isn't this a joke?

30:21.110 --> 30:23.040
How much is the hotel's profit now?

30:23.550 --> 30:25.070
18.6%.

30:25.640 --> 30:26.270
How much?

30:26.960 --> 30:28.790
18.6%

30:33.790 --> 30:35.510
It's because the follower effect

30:35.510 --> 30:36.640
brought by those two stars

30:36.640 --> 30:37.960
hasn't faded yet.

30:38.590 --> 30:40.400
The Chinese restaurant is doing well,

30:40.400 --> 30:42.030
so is the Jazz Bar.

30:42.440 --> 30:43.960
Now they are doing

30:43.960 --> 30:45.070
e-commerce live streaming.

30:45.070 --> 30:46.350
All right.

30:49.070 --> 30:50.920
Don't put ourselves down

30:50.920 --> 30:52.200
and boost his ego.

30:55.590 --> 30:56.240
Mr. Wei.

30:57.000 --> 30:59.000
The deadline for
the one-year VAM agreement

30:59.000 --> 31:00.680
is approaching.

31:01.240 --> 31:02.920
There

31:03.030 --> 31:05.110
is still quite a big gap.

31:05.350 --> 31:08.350
Ji Feng must also be eager to win,

31:08.350 --> 31:10.440
so he brought in such a big project.

31:10.880 --> 31:12.590
As for this event,

31:12.790 --> 31:14.350
it may look like a big deal,

31:14.550 --> 31:16.830
but it won't be that easy
for them to succeed.

31:16.830 --> 31:18.880
There must be plenty of loopholes.

31:19.030 --> 31:21.240
Rest assured. This time,

31:21.240 --> 31:22.970
we'll definitely find a chance

31:23.270 --> 31:25.160
to deal with Ji Feng

31:25.160 --> 31:26.590
and make him leave.

31:26.590 --> 31:27.840
This project

31:28.310 --> 31:30.440
is being led by Xu Miyu, right?

31:30.440 --> 31:31.240
Yeah.

31:31.550 --> 31:33.610
Isn't Xu Miyu under your management?

31:38.510 --> 31:39.590
I understand.

31:53.590 --> 31:54.510
Ms. Xu,

31:54.830 --> 31:56.960
you have a very good
relationship with Mr. Tan,

31:56.960 --> 31:59.880
so you will be responsible
for communicating with Party A.

31:59.880 --> 32:01.110
As for other chores,

32:01.110 --> 32:02.880
leave them to Ms. Lu.

32:03.590 --> 32:04.350
Ms. Lu,

32:05.270 --> 32:06.640
you are mainly responsible for

32:06.640 --> 32:09.640
the internal coordination
and division of labor in our hotel.

32:09.640 --> 32:10.590
Are you clear?

32:11.030 --> 32:11.920
Rest assured, Mr. Qian.

32:11.920 --> 32:13.510
I will definitely cooperate
with Ms. Xu

32:13.510 --> 32:15.510
and make this exhibition a success.

32:15.830 --> 32:16.640
Good.

32:28.400 --> 32:29.260
Here they come.

32:38.190 --> 32:39.160
Mr. Tan.

32:39.190 --> 32:40.240
Mr. Tan.

32:40.270 --> 32:41.110
Mr. Tan.

32:41.130 --> 32:41.740
Mr. Tan.

32:46.010 --> 32:46.620
Mr. Tan.

32:46.640 --> 32:47.440
Mr. Tan.

32:47.460 --> 32:48.010
Mr. Tan.

32:48.110 --> 32:50.220
Could you answer a few questions, Mr. Tan?

32:50.220 --> 32:50.910
Excuse me.

32:50.930 --> 32:51.640
Excuse me.

32:51.640 --> 32:52.620
Mr. Tan.

32:52.640 --> 32:53.790
Mr. Tan.

32:58.550 --> 32:59.680
Be careful. Watch out.

32:59.680 --> 33:00.920
Welcome, Mr. Tan.

33:00.920 --> 33:02.110
Thank you.

33:02.110 --> 33:03.110
This way, please.

33:05.270 --> 33:06.310
Mr. Tan.

33:06.310 --> 33:06.880
Mr. Tan.

33:06.880 --> 33:08.510
Could you answer a few questions, Mr. Tan?

33:08.510 --> 33:10.060
Mr. Tan.

33:11.000 --> 33:11.930
Okay. Thank you.

33:13.680 --> 33:15.680
First of all, I want to thank
all of you from the press

33:15.680 --> 33:18.640
for your support
and presence at our exhibition.

33:18.660 --> 33:19.260
Thank you.

33:19.840 --> 33:21.550
In the past,

33:21.550 --> 33:23.350
I worked as a curator

33:23.350 --> 33:25.400
all over the world,

33:25.400 --> 33:26.790
acting as a porter of artworks.

33:26.790 --> 33:28.160
This time, I'm very lucky

33:28.160 --> 33:30.350
to curate

33:30.350 --> 33:31.350
my own works.

33:31.350 --> 33:32.960
The curatorial context

33:33.240 --> 33:34.610
is a showcase

33:34.640 --> 33:36.880
of the achievements of my creative career

33:36.880 --> 33:38.350
over the past 30 years.

33:38.590 --> 33:41.830
From the immaturity of picking
up a brush for the first time,

33:41.830 --> 33:44.370
to the hesitation of leaving
the creative field,

33:44.370 --> 33:47.850
to today, when I finally
mustered the courage,

33:47.880 --> 33:49.160
as a painter,

33:49.270 --> 33:52.350
to exhibit my new works, which took me
two years, for the first time.

33:52.350 --> 33:53.070
I am very excited.

33:53.070 --> 33:54.350
I heard that originally,

33:54.350 --> 33:55.270
you planned to hold the exhibition
in Hong Kong.

33:55.270 --> 33:57.550
Why did you change your mind
at the last minute?

33:57.550 --> 33:58.890
Art is abstract,

33:59.110 --> 34:00.310
but life is concrete.

34:00.750 --> 34:02.510
What Purong Hotel gives me is

34:02.510 --> 34:04.240
concrete service experience,

34:04.310 --> 34:06.130
and concrete respect and understanding.

34:06.130 --> 34:07.450
It fully satisfies

34:07.480 --> 34:09.920
any of my pursuits in the abstract world.

34:10.190 --> 34:12.630
So, I have nothing to hesitate about.

34:43.070 --> 34:44.760
Before the exhibits are arranged
in the exhibition hall,

34:44.760 --> 34:46.960
they are all stored in the storage room.

34:47.030 --> 34:48.550
The three cameras inside
and outside the room

34:48.550 --> 34:49.400
have also been checked.

34:49.400 --> 34:50.480
There is no problem.

34:50.480 --> 34:52.070
The security department
will also arrange personnel

34:52.070 --> 34:54.030
to stand guard and patrol
around the clock,

34:54.030 --> 34:56.090
ensuring the safety of the exhibits.

34:56.880 --> 34:58.880
Thank you for your hard work, Ms. Lu.

35:10.070 --> 35:12.070
You're from
the Engineering Department, right?

35:12.070 --> 35:13.400
What are you doing here?

35:14.030 --> 35:14.700
Nothing.

35:15.070 --> 35:16.550
I just came to see

35:16.570 --> 35:18.550
when the exhibits can enter the hall.

35:18.550 --> 35:20.010
I'll get back to work then.

35:21.760 --> 35:23.670
Don't press this painting, you two.

35:23.670 --> 35:24.530
Put it upright.

35:30.000 --> 35:30.930
Okay. Thank you.

35:31.800 --> 35:33.270
Let me introduce you two.

35:33.440 --> 35:34.320
These are

35:34.320 --> 35:36.520
all my friends who fought alongside me.

35:36.630 --> 35:37.190
Dan,

35:37.440 --> 35:38.770
my publicity director,

35:39.000 --> 35:41.280
also the photographer
who knows me best.

35:41.590 --> 35:42.360
Skyler,

35:42.590 --> 35:43.670
my visual director.

35:43.670 --> 35:44.230
Every time

35:44.230 --> 35:45.280
we hold an exhibition,

35:45.280 --> 35:46.400
we break off our friendship.

35:46.400 --> 35:47.070
Every time we hold an exhibition,

35:47.070 --> 35:48.070
we break off our friendship.

35:48.070 --> 35:49.320
But every time we make up in the end.

35:49.320 --> 35:50.000
Well.

35:50.020 --> 35:51.590
Mainly because I can't outargue you.

35:51.590 --> 35:53.570
The only one who can is Cindy.

35:54.630 --> 35:55.880
The one who can outargue me

35:55.880 --> 35:57.100
is my chief butler

35:57.280 --> 35:58.670
and my financial director, Cindy.

35:58.670 --> 36:01.110
He is getting more and more willful now.

36:01.130 --> 36:02.730
I can't outargue him either.

36:03.710 --> 36:05.630
Thanks to Mr. Tan's willfulness,

36:05.630 --> 36:08.250
our hotel has such a precious opportunity.

36:09.000 --> 36:09.510
Come on.

36:09.510 --> 36:10.230
A toast to you.

36:10.230 --> 36:11.160
Okay, thank you.

36:11.440 --> 36:12.770
And a toast to everyone.

36:15.230 --> 36:16.070
Ms. Xu,

36:16.670 --> 36:19.400
we've only been communicating
via email before.

36:19.670 --> 36:21.530
I finally met you in person today.

36:22.150 --> 36:24.190
You are more beautiful

36:24.190 --> 36:25.790
and elegant than I imagined.

36:26.150 --> 36:27.230
Thank you, Ms. Lin.

36:27.230 --> 36:28.900
I'm looking forward to working with you.

36:28.900 --> 36:30.760
I'm looking forward to it as well.

36:46.920 --> 36:47.520
Thank you.

36:48.590 --> 36:49.400
It's you.

36:50.400 --> 36:52.630
It's my first time seeing Mr. Tan working.

36:52.630 --> 36:54.230
A bit different from what I imagined.

36:54.230 --> 36:55.780
Did it shock you?

36:56.800 --> 36:58.440
Actually, it makes it easier
to connect you

36:58.440 --> 36:59.440
with these artworks.

36:59.440 --> 37:00.570
Actually, these...

37:02.630 --> 37:03.510
Watch out!

37:09.070 --> 37:09.800
Are you okay?

37:10.550 --> 37:12.280
As long as the painting is fine.

37:12.400 --> 37:13.230
Mr. Ji, perfect timing.

37:13.230 --> 37:14.630
The setup is almost done.

37:14.630 --> 37:16.160
Shall we take a look around?

37:16.190 --> 37:16.810
Sure.

37:17.070 --> 37:17.590
Come on.

37:19.110 --> 37:20.590
This one is from the later period.

37:20.590 --> 37:22.480
This was with a friend.

37:22.710 --> 37:24.670
These works are so bold.

37:25.510 --> 37:26.150
Yes.

37:26.670 --> 37:28.750
This is the beginning of the story.

37:29.630 --> 37:31.920
It's like a child who just
came into this world,

37:31.920 --> 37:33.090
full of curiosity about everything,

37:33.090 --> 37:34.190
and charging recklessly.

37:34.190 --> 37:35.440
But if you look closely,

37:35.440 --> 37:36.760
you'll find the colors and lines

37:36.760 --> 37:38.490
are handled in such a naive way.

37:39.630 --> 37:41.070
As expected of Mr. Tan.

37:41.630 --> 37:43.630
The ingenuity is all in the details.

37:45.840 --> 37:47.960
Actually, this is my early work.

37:48.630 --> 37:49.590
I'll leave it to you two.

37:49.590 --> 37:50.550
I'll go keep an eye on things over there.

37:50.550 --> 37:51.110
Okay.

37:52.190 --> 37:53.150
Slow down a bit.

37:56.710 --> 37:58.710
Miyu is so careful and sharp.

37:58.710 --> 38:00.440
It's a pity she's not a curator.

38:02.230 --> 38:05.560
Are you trying to poach my staff
right in front of me, Mr. Tan?

38:05.760 --> 38:07.150
You're too sensitive, Mr. Ji.

38:07.150 --> 38:08.190
I dare not.

38:09.150 --> 38:09.840
Mr. Ji,

38:10.190 --> 38:12.070
What do you think of our exhibition?

38:12.070 --> 38:14.110
Is it worthy of Purong's banquet hall?

38:14.110 --> 38:15.110
You are too polite.

38:15.110 --> 38:16.630
Mr. Tan's art exhibition

38:16.630 --> 38:18.440
adds so much color

38:18.440 --> 38:20.280
to our hotel's banquet halls.

38:20.280 --> 38:21.190
You flatter me.

38:21.630 --> 38:24.400
However, I noticed the introduction
to each artwork

38:24.400 --> 38:26.670
uses a QR code.

38:25.210 --> 38:27.380
[Scan and check the profile of Tan Jizhou]

38:26.670 --> 38:27.960
But since our hotel

38:27.960 --> 38:29.630
has quite a few

38:29.630 --> 38:30.920
elderly guests,

38:31.190 --> 38:32.360
wouldn't this be

38:32.360 --> 38:33.590
unfriendly to them?

38:35.590 --> 38:37.800
I didn't think this through.

38:37.800 --> 38:39.720
But there's something
you don't know, Mr. Ji.

38:39.720 --> 38:42.030
Large blocks of text

38:42.030 --> 38:43.190
would be too complicated.

38:43.190 --> 38:44.590
For our exhibition,

38:44.610 --> 38:46.400
it would create a visual burden.

38:46.400 --> 38:47.840
The loss would outweigh the gain.

38:47.840 --> 38:49.570
Why don't we provide brochures

38:49.630 --> 38:50.800
for those who need them?

38:50.800 --> 38:51.800
What do you think?

38:53.070 --> 38:54.000
It makes sense.

38:55.110 --> 38:56.230
Anyway,

38:56.960 --> 38:58.890
holding this exhibition at Purong

38:59.280 --> 39:00.850
is my best decision.

39:01.590 --> 39:02.970
Pleasure working with you.

39:02.970 --> 39:04.510
Thank you for your trust, Mr. Tan.

39:04.510 --> 39:05.840
With our joint efforts,

39:05.960 --> 39:06.670
this art exhibition

39:06.670 --> 39:08.550
will definitely be a huge success.

39:08.550 --> 39:09.320
I believe so.

39:09.590 --> 39:10.400
Gentlemen,

39:10.400 --> 39:11.630
the main exhibit is up on the wall.

39:11.630 --> 39:12.670
Would you like to go and take a look?

39:12.670 --> 39:13.440
Let's take a look.

39:13.440 --> 39:14.150
Let's go.

39:21.320 --> 39:23.320
Is this the one to be unveiled tomorrow,

39:23.320 --> 39:24.480
the new work, "Time"?

39:24.480 --> 39:25.230
Exactly.

39:26.880 --> 39:28.190
In the past, when we talked about time,

39:28.190 --> 39:31.110
we always thought of the passing time.

39:31.110 --> 39:31.710
But

39:31.710 --> 39:34.230
after seeing so many works of Mr. Tan,

39:34.370 --> 39:35.070
I found that time

39:35.070 --> 39:36.800
brings all kinds of people

39:36.800 --> 39:38.480
into our lives.

39:38.480 --> 39:39.480
It's like each of us

39:39.480 --> 39:40.760
is a hotel,

39:41.000 --> 39:43.230
spending a lifetime
welcoming and seeing others off.

39:43.230 --> 39:45.110
There is laughter and regret.

39:45.760 --> 39:46.840
The most important thing

39:46.840 --> 39:49.590
is to cherish every encounter.

39:50.760 --> 39:52.560
I really like this explanation.

39:53.320 --> 39:54.110
Miyu.

39:55.190 --> 39:56.070
Thank you.

39:56.070 --> 39:57.840
Thank you for giving me

39:57.840 --> 39:59.450
such a wonderful possibility.

39:59.450 --> 40:00.640
So I hope

40:00.670 --> 40:03.070
you can cover it
with the curtain yourself.

40:03.400 --> 40:04.700
I'd be honored.

40:07.150 --> 40:07.630
Come on.

40:07.630 --> 40:08.480
Thank you.

40:14.920 --> 40:16.050
Come on. Be careful.

40:18.040 --> 40:18.990
Careful.

40:23.960 --> 40:25.280
Okay, slowly.

40:27.590 --> 40:28.440
Okay.

40:33.000 --> 40:33.630
Please.
